r />\n有幸見證呢套極左走火入魔之作<br />\n直頭係美國版既毛澤東傳記, 共產思想透過hollywood輸出國際<br />\n今鋪真係大撚獲<br />\n可以討論下"},{"pid":"2770928f4a734e570caff9a6224270faa34452e2","tid":2423898,"uid":59014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T07:30:18.000Z","msg":"整個疾病落去既劇本<br />\n一般比我感覺都較難感動、唔易代入<br />\n真人真事另計<br />\n<br />\n結論：鼓動真我 無得輸"},{"pid":"d1142ab899e168fbc5f00755f4461c282cf36758","tid":2423898,"uid":66893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6c29669a225c6e45110d0e51c37aa740dac9a91b","tid":2423898,"uid":250039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f1e2e59fe284810aabda6d5c42017f5a77286c36","tid":2423898,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T10:24:19.000Z","msg":"如果無黑豹，呢套男主角好大機會<br />\n而家個勢係追封影帝俾Wakanda Forever"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T12:40:17.000Z","msg":"仲有套Judas and the Black Messiah都係黑人片好有機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T11:15:40.000Z","msg":"兩個主角都淨男配角位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />split曬d votes。可能paul raci跑出<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}